data.description: Charming brick ranch offering not only the comforts of a well-designed home, but also the convenience of a prime location! With 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and over 1800 square feet of living space, this residence offers ample room for family, guests, or even a dedicated home office. When you step inside, you'll discover a tastefully designed interior that welcomes you with warmth and charm. The kitchen seamlessly connects the living spaces and offers plenty of cabinet and counter space. The dining room features a beautiful accent wall, adding a touch of character and creating a stylish focal point. Outdoors, you'll find a covered front porch and a great backyard space, perfect for entertaining!
